headline: Vestis (VSTS) Tops Q1 Earnings Estimates
summary: Vestis (VSTS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 16.67% and 0.43%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
